Ncomeka was last seen on Sunday by her mother at their home. She was wearing black denim jeans. Hayley was last seen on June 27 by her father at her home. Police say there was information that she might be in Kuilsriver as she was seen around the taxi rank. She was wearing pink takkies and blue jeans. Anyone with information or who has seen the missing teens is asked to contact Constable Barnardo at 082 469 3247 or 021 909 9500 at Mfuleni SAPS.